items.description:
- Measures the bias for news media outlets on Facebook;
- Complements the study on detecting bias of traditional news media websites;
- Some excellent pointers available in Related works. Summaries the prior research on quantifying bias of traditional news media sites;
- Provides a list of news media sites in Methodology section which can be helpful if you're planning to scrape news sites;
- Describes the 4 standard approach to measure bias related to a news media outlet;
- Demography based study of biased news media outlets
